17th March 2002
(Simon Horman)

     * 0.0.3
     - No Change


----------------------------------------------------------------------

24th March 2002
(Simon Horman)

     * 0.0.3beta2
     - Flush output if writing to a file descriptor.
       Fixes weirdness if a file descriptor gets shared between
       children.


